---
title: Butt Quarters

tags:
  - TAG1
  - TAG2

oneliner: Drop ten duence en a half
players: 2-15
tools:
  - 1 quarter per player
 
---
DESCRIPTION
Players place quarter in between their butt cheeks (pants on), and races to a destination without dropping the quarter from their bottom.
Variations on game includes; player must take multiple reverse steps as punishment for dropping the quarter; the game only ends with dropping quarters into a jar or basket; and play with other items of money such as pennies, or dollar bills.
